but you have to get a long.<br>
<br>
 Most people that have meet me in game knows I am not an uber roleplayer. Ok, almost non-existant. However, I strive to be respectfull of everyone I meet and interect with. I strive to have fun.  Someone comes up and says &quot;Hail, whatever, whatever&quot; most likely I will simply says &quot;hi&quot; and /smile. The few times I can think of I got out of line in game was with my own friends, which I regret. My how we can hurt the ones we love the most. <br>
<br>
 Note that if I wasn't at work with time on my hands, I wouldn't bother to respond to the nonsense this thread is about, the nonsense threads I and others have created concerning this issue. Personally, I think this same old crap is being dragged out of the wood works again cause the boards been dead lately. <br>
<br>
In conclusion to Mr. non-roleplayer hater,<br>
<br>
WE LOVE YOU! Let's play and have fun, apart.<br>
